[CENTER][SIZE="5"][COLOR=red]Team Bliss is not responsible in any way for anything that happens to your device in the process of installing[/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]
[CENTER]Please familiarize yourself with flashing and custom rom use before attempting to flash the rom.  Please make sure you download the correct version of Bliss for your specific device.  The links are labeled clearly.[/CENTER]  

[CENTER]Make sure you are rooted[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Make sure you have a custom recovery installed(TWRP is the preferred recovery)[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Download the latest Bliss Rom & the latest GApps package[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Boot into recovery[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Backup your current ROM[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Perform a FULL factory wipe and wipe/system and dalvik cache as a precaution[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Flash Bliss Rom[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Flash Google Apps package[/CENTER]
[CENTER]Flash Root of your choice(Unless OP states otherwise)[/CENTER]
[CENTER]First boot may take up to 10 minutes. This is due to Gapps and root optimization.[/CENTER]


[CENTER][IMG]https://i.imgur.com/CJQkPNY.png[/IMG][/CENTER]

[CENTER][*] Camera is broken <~~~~ example/placeholder[/CENTER]


[CENTER]If you have a major bug to report that has not been reported already, please take the following steps to report it to us.  It will save you and our team quite some time.[/CENTER]

[CENTER]Download the [URL="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nolanlawson.logcat&hl=en"][COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][U]Catlog[/U][/COLOR][/URL] app from the Play Store.[/CENTER]
[CENTER]There is also a donate version which you can purchase to show appreciation.[/CENTER]
[CENTER]After downloading the Catlog app, go to the app settings, and change the log level to Debug.[/CENTER]   
[CENTER]Clear all previous logs and take the exact steps to produce the error you are receiving.[/CENTER]  
[CENTER]As soon as you receive the error (probably a force close), go straight into Catlog and stop the log recording.[/CENTER]  
[CENTER]Copy and paste the entire log either to [URL="http://hastebin.com"][COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][U]Hastebin[/U][/COLOR][/URL] or [URL="http://pastebin.com"][COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][U]Pastebin[/U][/COLOR][/URL][/CENTER]   
[CENTER]Save the log, and copy and paste the link into the forum with a brief description of the error.[/CENTER]


